title: Jovs Screenwash 4 x 5 Litre - Screen Wash 20L for Cars, Windscreen - Concentrate & Effective to -4°C - Car Screen Washer Fluid & Windscreen Cleaner.
features: Our JOVS Ultra-concentrated screenwash concentrate 4 x 5L for economical use. One bottle makes enough car windscreen washer fluid to last a long time.
Effective to -4°C: De-icing power for winter use. Keep your windscreen wash clear even in freezing temperatures with our JOVS Concentrated Screen Wash 20 Litre.
Summer & Winter Use: One formula for all seasons. No need to switch between car screenwash for summer and winter.
Works in Hard & Soft Water: Cleans effectively regardless of your water type. This concentrated screenwash is perfect for any area.
Clean Solvent Formula: No unpleasant odours. Leave your windscreen clean and smear-free. This screenwash for cars uses a clean solvent formula.
Safe for Paintwork: Gentle formula that won't damage your car's paint. This car window washer fluid is safe for all vehicles.
Easy to Use: Simply dilute according to the included directions for summer, winter, or heavy winter conditions. This screen wash concentrate for cars is convenient and easy to use.
description: Powerful All-Season Screenwash Concentrate for Cars (Up to -4°C) Tired of running out of screenwash at the worst moment? Effective down to -4°C, it cuts through winter grime and de-ices your windscreen, keeping you safe on the road. No need to switch formulas! This all-season screenwash concentrate tackles summer bugs and winter frost with ease. The clean solvent formula leaves your windscreen sparkling clean and smear-free, with no unpleasant odours. Safe for all paintwork, this concentrated solution won't damage your car's finish. Simple to use! Just dilute according to the included instructions for summer, winter, or heavy winter conditions. This car window washer fluid is perfect for any area, working effectively in both hard and soft water.
